Interface Choice.Consequence<P,R>

  • Enclosing class:
    Choice<P,R>
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Choice.Consequence<P,R>
    Represents the preliminary stage of a Choice that is only missing a negative result.
